    rdfs:label 'Primary Center Id' ;
    rdfs:comment 'Foreign key linking to distribution.center. Business justification: In F&B supply chain, each customer ship-to location is assigned a primary serving distribution center for replenishment routing, delivery scheduling, and freight cost allocation. This DC-to-location a' ;
